      <title>英镑疲软提振出口商，富时 100 指数创下历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ftse-100-hits-first-record-high-since-may-after-pound-weakens</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦金融时报 100 指数周五创下历史新高，因为该股票指数的国际影响力使其免受英镑、英国政府债券和国内股票走弱所带来的大部分动荡的影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/ftse-100-hits-first-record-high-since-may-after-pound-weakens</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 09:03:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国交易员认为，英镑下跌抵消了债券市场 2023 年以来的最佳表现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国借贷成本即将创下一年多以来的最大三日跌幅，但由于对政府财政状况的担忧挥之不去，交易员认为英镑的走势不会有任何缓解。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-17/pound-falls-as-weak-retail-data-deals-fresh-blow-to-confidence</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 17 Jan 2025 07:45:29 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
